# Privacy Policy for Spendly

Last Updated: May 2026

Thank you for using Spendly.

Spendly is a personal finance and expense tracking application designed with privacy in mind. This Privacy Policy explains how the application handles information when you use the app.

## Information We Collect

Spendly does not require account creation, registration, or login.

All information entered into the app, including:

* Profile information
* Expense records
* Budget information
* Categories
* Split expense data
* Financial tracking information

is stored locally on your device.

Spendly does not collect, store, transmit, or share your personal financial data with external servers.

## Data Storage

All app data is stored locally on your device using secure device storage mechanisms.

Your information remains under your control and is not uploaded to any cloud service operated by Spendly.

## Data Sharing

Spendly does not sell, rent, trade, or share your personal information with third parties.

## Advertising

Spendly may display advertisements provided by third-party advertising partners.

These advertising providers may collect limited information necessary to deliver and measure advertisements in accordance with their own privacy policies.

Users should review the privacy policies of the advertising providers for additional information.

## Internet Connectivity

Certain optional features, such as advertisements or external links, may require an internet connection.

However, core expense tracking and budgeting functionality work offline without requiring an internet connection.

## Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect the information stored within the application.

Because all data is stored locally on your device, users are responsible for maintaining the security of their device.

## Children's Privacy

Spendly is not directed toward children under the age of 13.

We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

## Your Rights

Because Spendly stores data locally on your device:

* You can edit your information at any time.
* You can delete your information at any time.
* Uninstalling the application may remove locally stored data from your device.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time.

Any changes will be reflected by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this document.

